-06-04T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"1997年初，候任行政長官董建華曾經約見當時的支聯會主席司徒華，要求他停辦六四悼念活動；回歸後兩年也兩度約見司徒華，叫他放下六四包袱.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n董建華領先20年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f95de6d8843f7ff464662ce85a6c5212d20c02a","tid":270011,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFacebook post全部都係鬧佢地既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解鬧呢？<br />\n<br />\n維園已有大台, 想做支那人既咪去大台囉...</blockquote><br />\n行得太前 永遠都係比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"842ff2a1ab00b5fc843b84d16c896271435a913c","tid":270011,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nFacebook post全部都係鬧佢地既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中大一向係大中華基地<br />\n<br />\n個post好多人滑坡, 上綱上線    <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CUHK.SU/photos/a.416078851787863.103438.416069858455429/1483225301739874/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCUHK.SU%2Fphotos%2Fa.416078851787863.103438.416069858455429%2F1483225301739874%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=FWGQGMRI8%2BR9BXZI3QvkecmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=1e2d9804\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CUHK.SU/photos/a.416078851787863.103438.416069858455429/1483225301739874/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"422bf1636cdadfb6be8da951df5c5cc5d88ff340","tid":270011,"uid":5739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T05:22:25.000Z","msg":"我建議下年六四搞集會，悼念完之後大家嗌口號：香港獨立！"},{"pid":"0ad75cd6af5bea24a900992ef00eb83c133cd171","tid":270011,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c